project2adv

Class Account

  • java.lang.Object
    • project2adv.Account
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AccountInfo, TransactionHandler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Checking, Credit, Saving

    public abstract class Account
extends java.lang.Object
implements AccountInfo, TransactionHandler
    The Account abstract class represents a generic bank account with basic functionalities for handling deposits, withdrawals, and transfers. It maintains essential details such as account number, balance, and starting balance, and provides basic transaction logging capabilities.

    This class implements AccountInfo and TransactionHandler interfaces to define necessary methods for managing account-related actions. Specific account types should extend this class and implement additional details as needed.

    See Also:
    AccountInfo, TransactionHandler, TransactionLogger
